A very lovely experience. The art was wonderful and the music complemented the game beautifully, creating a nice atmosphere. I smiled a lot because of the characters & dialogue, yet my heart ached with the reality of what life can become. Overall, a great slice-of-life story-based visual novel.
Like most the other games the creator has made this one is also a very good happy/sad one. Honestly I recommend for sure cause it will make you feel a emotional spectrum :')

absolutely stunning artwork as always. I loved the simplicity of the style that made such beautiful moments stand out. I relate all too much with the fear of losing loved ones, but I know it is something I will have to deal with. thank you Angela for sharing this with the world, forever inspired by you üíï
